    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely stunning! I have babied this car since day one, and it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There isn't a single blemish on it, and the interior still has that fresh feel. I'm honestly a bit sad to let it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
